#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:518
msgid ""
"See Rancher documentation at <link xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs."
"rancher.com/v2.11\">https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.11</link>."
