#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1001
msgid ""
"This section describes how you can use Edge Virtualization to run virtual "
"machines on your edge nodes. Edge Virtualization is designed for lightweight "
"virtualization use-cases, where it is expected that a common workflow for "
"the deployment and management of both virtualized and containerized "
"applications will be utilized."
